<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Verify Email - Alumni Influencers</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 500px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .info { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Check Your Email</h1>

    <div class="info">
        <p>A verification link has been sent to <strong><%= email %></strong>.</p>
        <p>Please click the link in the email to verify your account.</p>
        <p>The link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <p><a href="/login">Back to Login</a></p>
</body>
</html>